snippet.title: BroManLegion
snippet.description: Hey What is up everybody! I make comedy videos for people on the internet and sometimes they're even funny. Currently my very achievable goal is to catch up to Mr Beast. I would've picked something harder but I figured it was a nice starting point. Fun fact, My real name is Brandon Boring and even though that name is 1000% Meme-able I decided not to use it for reasons you wont find out unless you subscribe. So, do that! Unless you're an extremely lame person with no sense of humor. Then you can just leave. PEACE! :D
